---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
 Custom Scan (DocumentDBApiCursorScan)
   Output: documentdb_api_internal.bson_dollar_project_find(document, '{ "b" : { "$numberInt" : "1" } }'::bson, '{ "a" : { "$numberInt" : "1" } }'::bson, '{ "now" : NOW_SYS_VARIABLE }'::bson)
   scanType: Primary Key Scan
   indexName: _id_
   ->  Index Scan using _id_ on documentdb_data.documents_2601 collection
