   ->  Bitmap Heap Scan on documentdb_data.documents_2602 collection_0_1
         Output: collection_0_1.document
         Recheck Cond: (collection_0_1.shard_key_value = '2602'::bigint)
         Filter: documentdb_api_internal.bson_dollar_lookup_join_filter(collection_0_1.document, documentdb_api_internal.bson_dollar_lookup_extract_filter_expression(collection.document, '{ "x" : "a" }'::bson), 'x'::text)
         ->  Bitmap Index Scan on _id_
               Index Cond: (collection_0_1.shard_key_value = '2602'::bigint)
(10 rows)

